  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "2. Add onion, ginger, and garlic. Cook until onion is translucent.",
    "3. Add cod fillets and cook until browned on both sides.",
    "4. Add tomato puree, curry powder, turmeric powder, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "5. Pour in coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "6. Reduce heat to low and let cook for 10-12 minutes or until cod is cooked through.",
    "7. Serve with Norwegian rustic bread for a delicious and filling meal."
